---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Luxury Landscaping in Paphos, Cyprus"
  description="Discover the Passion Behind Green Planet Gardening, a Family-Run Luxury Landscaping Company in Paphos, Cyprus"
  schemaType="AboutPage"
  faq={[
    { question: "Who are the founders of Green Planet Gardening?", answer: "Green Planet Gardening was founded by three brothers — Charalambos, Marios, and Angelos Knodaritis — in Paphos, Cyprus. Together with strategic advisor Fabio Fornaro, they bring over 10 years of combined experience in luxury landscaping, horticulture, and garden construction." },
    { question: "Where is Green Planet Gardening located?", answer: "Green Planet Gardening is based in Paphos, Cyprus, at Kerynias 5, Marathounta 8520. The company serves all regions of Cyprus including Limassol, Nicosia, Larnaca, and coastal resort areas." },
    { question: "What makes Green Planet Gardening different from other landscaping companies in Cyprus?", answer: "Green Planet Gardening is a family-run boutique landscaping company that takes on a limited number of projects each year. This ensures every garden receives maximum personal attention, craftsmanship, and design quality — something larger companies cannot offer." },
    { question: "Is Green Planet Gardening a registered company?", answer: "Yes. Green Planet Gardening operates as M.K. Green Planet Gardening and Landscaping Ltd, registered in Cyprus under company number HE402756 with the Cyprus Registrar of Companies." },
  ]}
>
  <Hero
    title="Three Brothers. One Vision."
    subtitle="A family united by earth, beauty, and the pursuit of perfection."
    backgroundImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600596542815-ffad4c1539a9?w=1920&q=80&fit=crop&crop=center"
    variant="inner"
  />

  <!-- Our Story — Split Section -->
  <section style="background:var(--color-cream);">
    <div class="split-section">
      <div class="split-image-wrapper">
        <div class="image-reveal">
          <img class="split-image" src="/images/projects/d50_6975.jpg" alt="Green Planet team sharing knowledge" loading="lazy" width="800" height="600" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="split-content">
        <div class="overlap-card">
          <span class="section-tag reveal">Our Story</span>
          <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1">Our Story</h2>
          <div class="section-line reveal reveal-delay-2"></div>
          <p class="section-text reveal reveal-delay-2">Green Planet Gardening was born from a simple yet profound idea — that a garden should be more than a collection of plants. It should be a living reflection of the soul of those who inhabit it.</p>
          <p class="section-text reveal reveal-delay-3" style="margin-top:16px;">We are three brothers who grew up with our hands in the earth, learning from our family that the greatest things in life are built with patience, passion, and care. When we founded Green Planet Gardening, we brought that philosophy with us: every garden we create is a personal commitment, a promise that grows with time.</p>
          <p class="section-text reveal reveal-delay-3" style="margin-top:16px;">For more than a decade, we have been designing, building, and nurturing <a href="/gallery" style="color:var(--color-gold);">luxury gardens across Cyprus</a> — from private hilltop villas in Paphos to beachfront resorts in Limassol. Our clients come to us because they see something different in our work: a soul that larger companies cannot offer.</p>
          <p class="section-text reveal reveal-delay-4" style="margin-top:16px;">We are not the biggest landscaping company in Cyprus. We never wanted to be. What we wanted — and what we have built — is a reputation for being the best at what we do. Every project is handcrafted. Every detail is intentional. Every garden is a masterpiece we are proud to sign.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background:var(--color-cream);">
    <div class="section-max section-center">
      <span class="section-tag reveal">Our Values</span>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1" style="text-align:center;">What We Stand For</h2>
      <div style="height:48px;"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="values-grid">
      {[
        { title: 'Passion', text: "We don't just work in gardens — we live for them. Every morning, we wake up excited to create something beautiful. This passion is the foundation of everything we do." },
        { title: 'Precision', text: "The difference between good and extraordinary lies in the details. We obsess over every stone placement, every plant arrangement, every shadow that falls across a pathway." },
        { title: 'Trust', text: "We never promise more than we can deliver. But we always deliver more than expected. Our word is our contract, and our reputation is built on keeping it." },
        { title: 'Timeless', text: "Trends come and go. We design gardens that transcend fashion — spaces that grow more beautiful with every passing year, becoming more themselves over time." },
      ].map((v, i) => (
        <div class="value-card reveal" style={`--i:${i}`}>
          <h3>{v.title}</h3>
          <p>{v.text}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background:white;">
    <div class="section-max section-center">
      <span class="section-tag reveal">The Family</span>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1" style="text-align:center;">Meet the Team</h2>
      <div style="height:48px;"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="team-grid">
      {[
        { name: 'Charalambos Knodaritis', role: 'Green Director & Landscape Architect', image: '/images/team/charalambos.jpg', quote: 'Every garden must have a soul, and that soul comes from the people who dream it.' },
        { name: 'Marios Knodaritis', role: 'Agronomist & Project Manager', image: '/images/team/marios.jpg', quote: 'Every plant has its own soul and its own place — the right plant in the right spot.' },
        { name: 'Angelos Knodaritis', role: 'Garden Construction & Irrigation Specialist', image: '/images/team/angelos.jpg', quote: 'Every project made with love lasts for years.' },
        { name: 'Fabio Fornaro', role: 'Strategic Business Consultant & Project Advisor', image: '/images/team/fabio.jpg', quote: "True quality is never a cost — it's an investment that lasts over time." },
      ].map((member) => (
        <div class="team-card reveal">
          <img src={member.image} alt={`${member.name}, ${member.role} at Green Planet Gardening Cyprus`} class="team-photo" loading="lazy" width="200" height="200" />
          <div class="team-name">{member.name}</div>
          <div class="team-role">{member.role}</div>
          <div class="team-quote">"{member.quote}"</div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background:var(--color-cream);">
    <div class="section-max section-center">
      <span class="section-tag reveal">Our Process</span>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1" style="text-align:center;">How We Work</h2>
      <div style="height:48px;"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="process-grid">
      {[
        { num: '01', title: 'Listen', text: 'Every project begins with a conversation. We visit your property, understand your vision, study the land, the light, the soil, and the story you want your garden to tell.' },
        { num: '02', title: 'Design', text: "We create a tailored landscape plan that balances your aesthetic desires with the realities of Cyprus's Mediterranean climate. Every plant, stone, and water feature is chosen with intention." },
        { num: '03', title: 'Build', text: 'Our skilled team brings the design to life with meticulous craftsmanship. We use only premium materials and proven techniques, treating your property with the respect it deserves.' },
        { num: '04', title: 'Nurture', text: "A garden is a living thing. We offer ongoing maintenance programmes to ensure your space grows more beautiful with every season, adapting to Cyprus's unique climate cycles." },
      ].map((s, i) => (
        <div class="process-step reveal" style={`--i:${i}`}>
          <div class="process-number">{s.num}</div>
          <h3>{s.title}</h3>
          <p>{s.text}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background:white;">
    <div class="section-max section-center">
      <span class="section-tag reveal">FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1" style="text-align:center;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div style="height:32px;"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Who are the founders of Green Planet Gardening?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">Green Planet Gardening was founded by three brothers — Charalambos, Marios, and Angelos Knodaritis — in Paphos, Cyprus. Together with strategic advisor Fabio Fornaro, they bring over 10 years of combined experience in luxury landscaping, horticulture, and garden construction.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Where is Green Planet Gardening located?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">Green Planet Gardening is based in Paphos, Cyprus, at Kerynias 5, Marathounta 8520. The company serves all regions of Cyprus including Limassol, Nicosia, Larnaca, and coastal resort areas.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What makes Green Planet Gardening different from other landscaping companies in Cyprus?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">Green Planet Gardening is a family-run boutique landscaping company that takes on a limited number of projects each year. This ensures every garden receives maximum personal attention, craftsmanship, and design quality — something larger companies cannot offer.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Is Green Planet Gardening a registered company?</summary>
        <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Green Planet Gardening operates as M.K. Green Planet Gardening and Landscaping Ltd, registered in Cyprus under company number HE402756 with the Cyprus Registrar of Companies.</div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="reveal">Ready to Start Your Garden Journey?</h2>
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Every great garden begins with a conversation. Tell us about your space, your vision, and your dreams — we'll take care of the rest.</p>
    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <a href="/contact" class="cta-btn">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
